  <h3> Guideligher </h3>
  <p> Guidelighter is a peer to peer marketplace for personal mentoring, advice and guidance.
  How often have you been in the situation that someone asked you for help with job or university applications or advice? If you have successfully gone through university and/or are currently in a job, chances are that you receive such requests for help a lot.</p>
  <p> On the other side of the medal: how often have you been in a situation wherein you needed help, advice or guidance? Who do you go to? Your personal network? Randomly reaching out to people on LinkedIn? Lucky if you have the network, lucky if you get the responses. We all need help at some point and we all are able to help at another. Guidelighter is the Marketplace that does just that putting you in touch with a guide, allowing you to offer your services, as a guide. </p>
  <p> We frequently publish on our blog at: <a href="http://www.guidelighter.net/" target="_blank"> www.guidelighter.net </a> </p> <br>

