  <h3> Oleg </h3>
  <p> Born in the Soviet Union, grew up in Germany, living in London. Working in finance, team-player, Karma-addict. Good at looking for trouble, better at finding solutions. Guidelighter is a brain-child that has been growing in my mind for years. It sometimes only takes the smallest of efforts to help a person in a major way. Why don’t more people do it then? Helping starts in your day to day. Let’s hack helping and raise people’s awareness of how we can make each other’s lives easier! <br> <br> I studied Politics and International Relations at Royal Holloway followed by an MPhil in International Relations at Oxford from whereon I joined Citigroup’s Corporate Banking group. I covered EMEA corporates across all industries as part of an Analyst Pool before moving into the team of Citigroup’s Portfolio Head for Global Public Sector. In that function I now cover sovereign and sovereign-owned entity risk around the world. I co-founded Guidelighter to combine my work in finance with my passion to help people fulfil their career dreams.
  </p> <br>


